Quickstrike:



"Yeah," Quickstrike replied to Tarantulas through comm-link. "Another 
meetin'? She oughta tell me 'bout this stuff." He didn't catch onto 
the spider's attempt to make him edgy over her. "By th' way, whaddya 
wanna do wit' that rat? He may gots himself uh Pred signature, but he 
sure ain't no Pred!"
